@startuml
title Recipe suggestions - exact function calls

actor User
participant "RecipeSuggestionsPage" as SuggestionsPage
participant "useCreateRecipeSuggestionsMutation()" as SuggestionMutation
participant "createRecipeSuggestions()" as SuggestionApi
participant "buildApiUrl()" as BuildApiUrl
participant "RecipeSuggestionsController\nPOST /api/recipe-suggestions" as SuggestionsEndpoint
participant "RecipeSuggestionService.CreateSuggestions()" as SuggestionService

User -> SuggestionsPage : Open /suggest
User -> SuggestionsPage : Enter ingredients, servings, max time
SuggestionsPage -> SuggestionMutation : mutateAsync(input)
SuggestionMutation -> SuggestionApi : createRecipeSuggestions(input)

alt Mock mode
  SuggestionApi --> SuggestionMutation : empty suggestion response
else HTTP mode
  SuggestionApi -> BuildApiUrl : buildApiUrl("/api/recipe-suggestions")
  BuildApiUrl --> SuggestionApi : absolute URL
  SuggestionApi -> SuggestionsEndpoint : POST /api/recipe-suggestions
  SuggestionsEndpoint -> SuggestionService : CreateSuggestions(request)
  SuggestionService --> SuggestionsEndpoint : RecipeSuggestionResponse
  SuggestionsEndpoint --> SuggestionApi : 200 OK + JSON
  SuggestionApi --> SuggestionMutation : RecipeSuggestionResponse
end

SuggestionMutation --> SuggestionsPage : result or error
SuggestionsPage --> User : Render suggestions, empty state, or error

@enduml
